title: Chamizal National Memorial: Web Rangers
body: Web Rangers           Join Chami and his friends on three adventures as you learn more about Chamizal National Memorial and the National Park Service. Click on the "Let's Begin" button to start the adventures!  Si desea ver este sitio en español, haga Clic aquí.       Receive a password at the end of each chapter to go on to the next!(object placeholder)       Web Ranger Certificate Print your Web Ranger Certificate! Be sure to have your password with you.   NPS Web Rangers The National Park Service has created a site where all our visitors can become Junior Web Rangers! Click here to go to a new page.
